trans-unit.source: Provides methods and properties that manage the major and minor grids of <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder metoder og egenskaper som styrer overordnede og underordnede rutenett for <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class provides the functionality for the grids on the chart, and is exposed using the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.MajorGrid%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.MinorGrid%2A> properties of each <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen gir funksjonaliteten for rutenett på diagrammet, og er utsatt ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.MajorGrid%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.MinorGrid%2A>Egenskaper for hver <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.MinorGrid%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.MajorGrid%2A>

trans-unit.source: Major grid lines by default do not have their <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.Interval%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A> properties set.
trans-unit.target: Hoved rutenett som standard har ikke de <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.Interval%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A>angitt egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffset%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.Interval%2A>

trans-unit.source: When these properties for major grid lines are not set, the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control determines the appropriate values for grid lines automatically.
trans-unit.target: Når disse egenskapene for store rutenett er ikke, den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontrollen bestemmer de riktige verdiene for rutenett automatisk.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: The axis and its minor grid lines by default have their <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.Interval%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A> properties set to **Auto** (0).
trans-unit.target: Den og de underordnede rutenett som standard har sine <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.Interval%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffset%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A>egenskapene til **automatisk** (0).</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffset%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.Interval%2A>

trans-unit.source: If axis labels or minor grid lines are enabled and these properties are not modified, the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control automatically determines how often to draw the minor grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Hvis akseetiketter eller underordnet rutenett er aktivert, og disse egenskapene er ikke endret, den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontrollen automatisk bestemmer hvor ofte skal tegne underordnede rutenettlinjene.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: Axis grids: - Can be enabled or disabled.
trans-unit.target: Akse rutenett: – kan være aktivert eller deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: - Have a starting point that determines where they are first drawn.
trans-unit.target: -Har utgangspunkt som bestemmer hvor de første tegnes.

trans-unit.source: - Display lines that can be set for style, width and color.
trans-unit.target: – Vis linjene som kan angis for stil, bredde og farge.

trans-unit.source: - Can have either automatic intervals, or intervals that are set manually.
trans-unit.target: – Kan ha automatisk intervaller eller intervaller som er angitt manuelt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a flag that determines whether major or minor grid lines are enabled.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et flagg som bestemmer om overordnet eller underordnet rutenett er aktivert.

trans-unit.source: Major and minor grids are visible when enabled, and not visible when disabled.
trans-unit.target: Overordnede og underordnede rutenett er synlige når aktivert, og er ikke synlig når deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: Tick marks will not be displayed if disabled.
trans-unit.target: Aksemerker vises ikke hvis deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: You can disable tick marks by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMark.TickMarkStyle%2A> property to <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMarkStyle>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan deaktivere aksemerkene ved angivelse av <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMark.TickMarkStyle%2A>egenskapen <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMarkStyle>.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMarkStyle> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.TickMark.TickMarkStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref> if enabled, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if disabled.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_True" name="True" href=""></xref>Hvis aktivert, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis deaktivert.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> for major grid objects and <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> for minor grid objects.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> for rutenett hoved-objekter og <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> for rutenett underordnede objekter.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the interval between major or minor grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir intervallet mellom overordnet eller underordnet rutenettlinjene.

trans-unit.source: By default this property is not set for axis labels, major tick marks and major grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er ikke angitt for akseetiketter, aksemerker og hoved rutenett som standard.

trans-unit.source: If it is not set—either by default, by explicitly using <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> at design time, or by assigning a value of <xref:System.Double.NaN> at run time—the actual value of this property is determined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Interval%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object to which the chart element, such as a grid line or tick mark, belongs.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det ikke er angitt, som standard via eksplisitt <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>under utformingen, eller ved å tilordne en verdi for <xref:System.Double.NaN>ved kjøretid – den faktiske verdien for egenskapen avgjøres av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Interval%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objekt som diagramelement, for eksempel et rutenett linje eller aksemerkene merke tilhører.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Interval%2A> </xref:System.Double.NaN> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>

trans-unit.source: The interval of minor tick marks and grid lines is never affected by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Interval%2A> property value.
trans-unit.target: Intervallet for aksemerker på delskala og rutenett aldri påvirkes av de <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Interval%2A>egenskapsverdi.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.Interval%2A>

trans-unit.source: The interval is measured in axis units, and determines how often an applicable chart element is drawn.
trans-unit.target: Intervallet måles i aksen enheter, og bestemmer hvor ofte en gjelder diagramelementet er tegnet.

trans-unit.source: For example, suppose a column chart has an X axis step of 1 (that is, 1, 2, 3, 4, and so forth); if you set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.Interval%2A> property for the X axis to 2, an axis label will be displayed for every other column.
trans-unit.target: Sett et stolpediagram har et X-aksen trinn 1 (det vil si 1, 2, 3, 4, og så videre); Hvis du angir den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.Interval%2A>egenskapen for X-aksen til 2, vises en akseetikett for hver kolonne.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.Interval%2A>

trans-unit.source: The same holds true for all applicable chart elements.
trans-unit.target: Det samme gjelder for alle aktuelle diagramelementer.

trans-unit.source: In other words, if in the previous example strip lines were being used, with an <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.IntervalOffset%2A> of 0.5, and their <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.Interval%2A> property was 2, a strip line would be displayed at 0.5, 2.5, 4.5, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Med andre ord, hvis linjer ble brukt i den forrige eksemplet stripen, med en <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.IntervalOffset%2A>på 0,5, og deres <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.Interval%2A>egenskapen 2 ved stripe-linje skal vises for 0,5, 2.5, 4.5 og så videre.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.Interval%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.StripLine.IntervalOffset%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you set a chart element `Interval` property to zero, an interval will be automatically determined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir et diagramelement `Interval` -egenskapen til null, et intervall automatisk bestemmes av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value that represents the interval between grid lines.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> verdi som representerer intervallet mellom rutenettlinjene.

trans-unit.source: By default, the value is not set (<xref:System.Double>) for major grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Som standard verdien er ikke angitt (<xref:System.Double>) for store rutenettlinjene.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: For minor grid lines, the default value is zero (0).
trans-unit.target: For underordnede rutenett er standardverdien null (0).

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the offset of grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir forskyvningen for rutenettlinjene.

trans-unit.source: By default this property is not set for axis labels, major tick marks and major grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er ikke angitt for akseetiketter, aksemerker og hoved rutenett som standard.

trans-unit.source: If it is not set—either by default, by explicitly specifying "Not Set"at design time, or by assigning it a value of <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> at run time—the actual value of this property is determined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffset%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object that the chart element, such as a grid line or a tick mark, belongs to.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det ikke er angitt, som standard, ved å angi eksplisitt "Er ikke angitt" under utformingen eller ved å tilordne en verdi for <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>ved kjøretid – den faktiske verdien for egenskapen avgjøres av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffset%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objekt som tilhører diagramelement, for eksempel et rutenett eller et aksemerke.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffset%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>

trans-unit.source: The interval offset of minor tick marks and grid lines is never affected by the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffset%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object.
trans-unit.target: Intervallforskyvning for aksemerker på delskala og rutenett aldri er berørt av verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffset%2A>-egenskapen til det <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffset%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A> property setting defines the units of measurement of the offset.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A>egenskapsinnstillingen definerer målenheten for forskyvningen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalOffsetType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The IntervalOffset can be a negative value.
trans-unit.target: IntervalOffset kan være en negativ verdi.

trans-unit.source: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""></xref> value that represents the interval offset.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_double" name="double" href=""> </xref> verdi som representerer intervallforskyvning.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the interval offset type of major and minor grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir forskyvningen intervalltypen for overordnede og underordnede rutenettlinjene.

trans-unit.source: By default this property is not set for axis labels, major tick marks and major grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er ikke angitt for akseetiketter, aksemerker og hoved rutenett som standard.

trans-unit.source: If it is not set—either by default, by explicitly specifying "Not Set" at design time, or by assigning it a value of <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> at run time—the actual value of this property is determined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object that the chart element—a grid line or tick mark, for example—belongs to.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det ikke er angitt, som standard, ved å angi eksplisitt "Er ikke angitt" under utformingen eller ved å tilordne en verdi for <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>ved kjøretid – den faktiske verdien for egenskapen bestemmes av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objekt som diagramelementet – rutenett eller merke, for eksempel for aksemerker – tilhører.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>

trans-unit.source: The interval offset type of minor tick marks and grid lines is never affected by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A> property value.
trans-unit.target: Intervalltypen forskyvningen for aksemerker på delskala og rutenett aldri påvirkes av de <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A>egenskapsverdi.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A>

trans-unit.source: If this interval offset type is set to <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>, the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A> property will be used.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne type intervallforskyvning er satt til <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>, <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A>egenskapen vil bli brukt.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Grid.IntervalType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"></xref> enumeration value that indicates the interval type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"> </xref> nummereringsverdi som angir intervalltypen.

trans-unit.source: By default it is not set for major grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Som standard er det ikke angis for hoved rutenettlinjene.

trans-unit.source: The default value for minor grid lines is <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien for underordnede rutenettlinjene <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the interval type for major or minor grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir intervalltypen for overordnet eller underordnet rutenettlinjene.

trans-unit.source: By default this property is not set for axis labels, major tick marks and major grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er ikke angitt for akseetiketter, aksemerker og hoved rutenett som standard.

trans-unit.source: If it is not set—either by default, by explicitly using "Not Set" at design time, or by assigning it a value of <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType> at run time— the actual value of this property is determined by the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> object that the chart element—a grid line or tick mark, for example—belongs to.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det ikke er angitt, enten som standard via eksplisitt "Er ikke angitt" under utformingen eller ved å tilordne en verdi for <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>ved kjøretid – den faktiske verdien for egenskapen bestemmes av den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis>objekt som diagramelementet – rutenett eller merke, for eksempel for aksemerker – tilhører.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalOffsetType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>

trans-unit.source: The interval type of minor tick marks and grid lines is never affected by the value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Intervalltypen for aksemerker på delskala og rutenett aldri er berørt av verdien for den <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalType%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Axis.IntervalType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Interval types can be set to <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>; the type of interval then depends on either the X-values or Y-values of the plotted <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPoint> objects, depending on which axis the applicable elements belong to.
trans-unit.target: Intervallet typer kan settes til <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>; intervalltypen deretter avhenger av den X-verdier eller Y-verdier for den tegnede <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPoint>objekter, avhengig av hvilken akse gjelder elementene tilhører.</xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DataPoint> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType>

trans-unit.source: Setting the IntervalType property for a value axis will only have an effect if the values of the data points are <xref:System.DateTime> or `double` values.
trans-unit.target: Angi egenskapen IntervalType for en verdiakse får bare en effekt hvis verdiene for datapunktene er <xref:System.DateTime>eller `double` verdier.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Also, the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A> property of the plotted <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> must be set to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType>.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg til <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A>, eller <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A>egenskapen for den tegnede <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>må settes til <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType>eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Setting the IntervalType property for a categorical axis will only have an effect if the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A> property (or <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A> property, depending on the axis in question) of the plotted <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> object is either <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType>.
trans-unit.target: Angi egenskapen IntervalType for en kategoriske akse får bare en effekt hvis det <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A>egenskapen (eller <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A>egenskapen, avhengig av den aktuelle aksen) for den tegnede <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series>objektet er enten <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType>eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartValueType> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.YValueType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Series.XValueType%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Sunday is considered the first day of the week.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Søndag anses som den første dagen i uken.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"></xref> enumeration value that indicates the interval type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"> </xref> nummereringsverdi som angir intervalltypen.

trans-unit.source: By default it is not set for axis labels, major tick marks and major grid lines, by using the <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"></xref> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: Som standard det ikke er angitt for akseetiketter, aksemerker og hoved rutenettlinjene ved å bruke den <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"> </xref> listeverdi.

trans-unit.source: The default value for minor tick marks and grid lines is <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien for aksemerker på delskala og rutenettlinjene <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.DateTimeIntervalType"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line color of a grid.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir linjefargen på et rutenett.

trans-unit.source: The LineColor property is used to specify the color of major and minor tick marks or grids.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen LineColor brukes til å angi fargen på overordnede og underordnede aksemerkene eller rutenett.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Color"></xref> object.

trans-unit.source: The default value is <xref:System.Drawing.Color.Black*>.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er <xref:System.Drawing.Color.Black*>.</xref:System.Drawing.Color.Black*>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line style of a grid.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir linjestilen for et rutenett.

trans-unit.source: The LineDashStyle property can be used to specify the line style of major and minor tick marks or grids.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen LineDashStyle kan brukes til å angi linjestilen for overordnede og underordnede aksemerkene eller rutenett.

trans-unit.source: The line can be solid, dotted, and so forth.
trans-unit.target: Linjen kan være fylt prikket og så videre.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartDashStyle"></xref> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartDashStyle"> </xref> listeverdi.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartDashStyle"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref href="System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartDashStyle"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the line width of major and minor grid lines.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir tykkelsen på overordnede og underordnede rutenettlinjene.

trans-unit.source: The LineWidth property can be used to specify the line width, in pixels, of major and minor tick marks or grids.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen LineWidth kan brukes til å angi linjetykkelsen på overordnede og underordnede aksemerkene eller rutenett i piksler.

trans-unit.source: An <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""></xref> that represents the line width in pixels.
trans-unit.target: En <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""> </xref> som representerer linjetykkelse i piksler.

trans-unit.source: The default value is one (1).
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er én (1).
